  "title": "Administrative Executive (Scheduling Dept)",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Role:</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Schedule audit and training assignments</li>\n  <li>Co-ordinate with auditors and clients regarding audit assignments</li>\n  <li>Compile and maintain clients' records</li>\n  <li>Update and maintain accurate client database</li>\n  <li>Review clients' application and audit reports</li>\n  <li>Issuance certicates to clients</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Requirement:</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Those with minimum 2 years working experience in customer service will be added advantageous</li>\n  <li>Familiar with Microsoft Words, Excel &amp; Outlook</li>\n  <li>Possess good interpersonal and organizational skills</li>\n</ul>",
