    "uen": "200208777D",
    "description": "<p>GUARDIAN INDEPENDENT CERTIFICATION PTE. LTD.</p>\n<p>Established in 2002 in Singapore, Guardian Independent Certification Pte Ltd (GIC Pte Ltd) is a professional service firm offers comprehensive range of conformity assessments and training services in the areas of Quality, Environmental, Health &amp; Safety and Food Safety Management Systems.</p>\n<p>It is a wholly-owned company of GIC Group, which also owns GIC Ltd - an internationally recognized professional certification body registered in the United Kingdom and accredited by the highly regarded accreditation body - United Kingdom Accreditation Service (UKAS) and Australia and New Zealand Accreditation Body (JASANZ).</p>\n<p>Through its qualified workforce - auditor and expert knowledge and professionalism, GIC Pte Ltd has guided many organizations towards the successful attainment of accredited certification for their management systems, and has assisted many different organizations increased profitability, motivated their staff and ultimately, gained a vital competitive edge.</p>\n<p>GIC Pte Ltd's client base cuts across all industry sectors. Irrespective of the nature or size of your organization, establishing close and open working relationships is fundamental to GIC's service philosophy. With our proactive approach in understanding clients' needs, GIC Pte Ltd is able to deliver added value and guarantee successful certification.</p>\n<p>In addition, GIC Pte Ltd provides a wide range of management system related training courses including IRCA (International Register of Certified Auditors) approved training – QMS Lead Auditor Course, that help you become registered to professional qualification which is recognized world-wide.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Company website: https://gicgrp.com/sg</p>",
